data.description: WELCOME HOME! This impressive 3,381 sq. ft. estate home offers 5 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms in the Gated Golf Course community of Northshore at Lake Hart in Lake Nona. This well detailed residence offers spectacular curb appeal with its wide lot and 3 car garage with no rear neighbors. The Foyer greets you with high ceilings and an open concept split floorplan. The Flex area off the foyer is perfect for an office, art studio or den. The large open Dining Room is exceptional for hosting your friends and family, and directly ahead the spacious Living Room is centrally located for entertaining. The Gourmet Kitchen is ideal for any aspiring chef with quartz countertops, upgraded 42" wood cabinetry, island with additional cabinetry, backsplash, premium stainless-steel appliances, walk-in pantry and spacious eat-in area. The adjacent open Great Room is perfect for movie night, the big game and spending time with family and friends . The large main floor Primary Suite is your sanctuary for relaxation, a spacious retreat with a separate lounge area. The Dual Primary Closets will meet your complete wardrobe needs. The Primary Bathroom has 2 Vanities, a separate walk-in shower and a deep Garden Tub to relax in a bubble bath. Bedroom 2 and 3 share one of several Main Bathrooms with vanity, separate water closet and bath/shower combo. Bedroom 4 is conveniently located to the other Main Bathroom with vanity and bath/shower combo  Up the stairs is Bedroom 5 with its own full Ensuite Bathroom. The laundry room is conveniently located and provides access to the 3 car garage with ample storage area. Step out to the spacious covered lanai with Outdoor Kitchen and cool off in the amazing Pool surrounded by Nature at its best. Living in this beautiful community you also enjoy access to the community pool, Gazebo on the water, fitness center, basketball court, tennis courts, dog park, and more! Close to the best that Lake Nona and Central Florida have to offer including Disney, Universal, Boxi Park, restaurants, shopping and so much more. Schedule your private showing today. ALL FURNITURE AND FURNISHINGS ARE INCLUDED.
